# Updater signing keys — NEVER commit the private key.
# .updater-secrets/ holds the local copy of the private key + passphrase.
# Put the same values into GitHub repository secrets (TAURI_SIGNING_PRIVATE_KEY,
# TAURI_SIGNING_PRIVATE_KEY_PASSWORD) for the release workflow to use.
.updater-secrets/

